title: Thomas D'Innocenzi
text: Working with Atheneum professionals has been throughly professional and engaging, allowing for creating thinking to the needs of the client. It has been a pleasure to work with other professionals that are focused, fast-paced, yet genuinely eager to meet the consulting demands of the customer. Critical thinking is embraced, and the attitude of Atheneum professionals has been open and engaging.
